_sText:
This map has many fun new things in it.
2 secret ways to get into the ct spawn.
- 1 is by the big portal(you have to croch and maze ur way in).
- 2 on top of the second cell bed.

1 heal room 
- It is the fountain and statue(just stand in the area of thim).

1 solitary

1 disco room
- You can control the lights/music.
- You can lock/unlock the dj door.

4 sniper towers.

1 hidden usp in one of the cells.
